name: Princess Peach - Nintendo The Super Mario Bros. Movie (Illumination Entertainment Animation Style)
description:
I trained with 256 images, about 1/3 with full body images 2/3 closeups from all angles. For the training I mainly used screenshots from "The Super Mario Bros. Movie" and a few Promo pictures from the internet. I used Normal Pink Dress, Blue Dress, Racing Jumpsuit, Wedding Dress from the movie, for more variety in her clothing. See outfit prompts for more information

Please take a look at more LoRAs made by me

This LoRA works with most models.

These models are tested and work with this LoRA:

"Lyriel", "DucHaitenDreamWorld", "ReV Animated", "Disney Pixar Cartoon Type A", "cartoonish", "animatrix" and "Mistoon_Amethyst"

Trigger Words: PrincessPeach, Jumpsuit, WeddingDress,

Best LoRA prompts:

  • Extra Networks Multiplier for this LoRA set to "0.6 - 0.8" Gives the best results in my opinion

Outfit pompts:

  • Normal Pink Dress: PrincessPeach, (pink dress), blue eyes, choker, glossy lips, pink lips,

  • Blue Dress: PrincessPeach, (blue dress:1.4), blue eyes, choker, glossy lips, pink lips,

  • Racing Jumpsuit: PrincessPeach, (Jumpsuit:1.2), blue eyes, choker, glossy lips, pink lips,

  • Wedding Dress: PrincessPeach, (WeddingDress:1.2), (Veil:1.3), blue eyes, choker, glossy lips, pink lips,

Feel free to share your results here. Would be happy to see what you create
